    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克（Lutnick</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/lutnick-says-trump-plan-aims-to-knock-down-non-tariff-barriers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）说，其他经济体不会采用美国农产品，“这必须结束”。他还说，需要拆除非关税贸易壁垒。卢特尼克（Lutnick）谈到“彭博监视”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/lutnick-says-trump-plan-aims-to-knock-down-non-tariff-barriers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税和欧佩克+输出加息伤害市场时，石油暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/surprise-opec-hike-and-growth-sapping-tariffs-send-oil-plunging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易关税和欧佩克+决定增加产出速度的双胞胎袭击之后，石油在2023年以来最多，这比以前宣布的更快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/surprise-opec-hike-and-growth-sapping-tariffs-send-oil-plunging</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
