      <title>随着进口的升高，美国贸易差距在进出口增长时缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-trade-gap-shrinks-on-export-boost-as-imports-stay-elevated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国贸易赤字从今年年初的记录开始缩减，因为强劲的出口削弱了在特朗普政府的大量关税之前急于获得商品和材料的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-trade-gap-shrinks-on-export-boost-as-imports-stay-elevated</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
